---
title: Hearty Moroccan Lentil, Currant & Veggie Stew with Mash & Slivered Almonds
description: Bring the warm Moroccan flavours to your table in the form of a stew packed on top of a blanket of mashed potato. There’s the comforting addition of lentils, spices and the pop of currants is everything this stew needs to end a long day.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
